Now what I mean by that is that for an idea
to stick in someone else's mind the first

00:28:28.230 --> 00:28:33.600
thing we wanna share with someone else is
the essence of the idea, that could be the

00:28:33.600 --> 00:28:38.049
form, but it's the essence of it. What is
my idea in the end of the day really about?

00:28:38.049 --> 00:28:42.510
Now I have done some work with the Navy and
what was fascinating to me is there I was

00:28:42.510 --> 00:28:45.690
at the Naval War College and I was working
